<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">rich</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE_DESC">countries</ENAMEX> would have to be losing jobs and productive capacity and
getting richer at the same time, even as developing <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE_DESC">countries</ENAMEX> would be taking
